high_descs: Turn right and walk towards the wall, then hang a left and walk up to the small black table.
Pick up the set of keys off of the small black table.
Turn left and walk across the room, then turn right and walk up to the tall white shelving unit.
Put the set of keys in the cardboard box that is on the bottom shelf in front of you.
Pick up the cardboard box with the keys in it off of the shelf.
Walk over to the blue chair with the yellow pillow on it that is behind you.
Put the cardboard box with the keys in it on the seat of the blue chair to the right of the yellow pillow.
anns.task_desc: Put a cardboard box with keys in it on the seat of a blue chair.

high_descs: Turn right to walk towards the black side table.
Pick up the keys on the black side table.
Turn left to walk to the white bookcase on the right of the other white bookcase.
Set the keys down in a box on the bottom shelf of the bookcase.
Pick up the box with the keys in it from the bottom shelf of the white bookcase.
Turn around and walk forward towards the blue armchair.
Set the box with the keys in it down on the seat of the blue armchair.
anns.task_desc: Put keys in a box to put on the blue armchair.

high_descs: Turn to the right and then face the black table on the left.
Pick up the keys from the center of the black table.
Carry the keys and turn to the left. Turn right to face the tall white shelf.
Place the keys in the box on the shelf.
Pick up the box from the shelf.
Carry the box and turn to the right, then right again. Move to the blue chair.
Place the box on the blue chair, to the right side.
anns.task_desc: Move a box and keys to the blue chair.
